sh"},{"pid":"f5b315f9ce465be38d2492894b8b8539b72b1f2d","tid":1560462,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB/TG搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"807fa94f1bb697fb798176ba559031669a5dac00","tid":1560462,"uid":91558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:31:32.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請即參與：#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1560141/page/1</a><br />\n已有手足推緊hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n向外國人宣傳警暴！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link